  "description": {
    "zh": "想要获得 AK-12 突击步枪和 RPK-16 机枪的使用权？那就出点力吧，怎么样？\n\n有人下了订单。AK 要求可折叠、装有消音器、普通手电、Zenit Perst-3战术设备，射程要在 600 米以上，并配备 AK-74 的塑料弹匣。RPK 要求装反射式瞄具和战术配件，弹容量至少 90 发。其余细节我都列好了。\n\nAK-12 要求：\n - 后坐力总和小于 360\n - 重量小于 5.2 公斤\n - 人机功效 51 或更高\n - 耐久度至少 95 %\n - 弹匣容量 30 或更多\n - 宽度占用 5格 或更少\n - “射击场”距离 600米 或更多\n - 任意 独立战术手电筒\n - 任意 消音器\n - Zenit Perst-3战术设备\n - 6L20 5.45x39 30发AK-74兼容弹匣\n\nRPK-16 要求：\n - 后坐力总和小于 225\n - 重量小于 4.6 公斤\n - 人机功效 49 或更高\n - 耐久度至少 95 %\n - 弹匣容量 90 或更多\n - 任意 准直式瞄具\n - 任意 战术设备",
    "en": "If you want to receive access to AK-12 assault rifles and RPK-16 machineguns, now is the time to help out. Interested?\n\nSomeone requested these weapons, make sure the AK can be folded and is suppressed, it also needs a ordinary flashlight and a Zenit Perst-3 laser, a sighting range of about six-hundred meters or more, and it needs to have a normal AK-74 bakelite magazine. The RPK requires just a reflex sight and a tactical device, and also needs to hold at least ninety rounds or more. Further details will be written down for you again.\n\nAK-12 Requirements :\n - Recoil Sum less than 360\n - Weight less than 5.2 KG\n - Ergonomics 51 or higher\n - Durability higher than 95 %\n - Magazine Capacity of 30 or more\n - Width of 5 slots or less\n - Sighting Range of 600 Meters or more\n - A Standalone Flashlight\n - A Silencer\n - Zenit Perst-3 Tactical Device\n - AK-74 5.45x39 6L20 30-Round Magazine\n\nRPK-16 Requirements :\n - Recoil Sum less than 225\n - Weight less than 4.6 KG\n - Ergonomics 49 or higher\n - Durability higher than 95 %\n - Magazine Capacity of 90 or more\n - A Collimator\n - A Tactical Device"
  },
